      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Apology and Special Offer for Your Espresso Machine Order\n\nDear [Customer Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to express our sincerest apologies for the delay in the delivery of your recently purchased espresso machine. We understand how valuable your time is, and we regret any inconvenience this may have caused.\n\nAs a valued customer, we would like to offer you a 10% discount on your next order or free shipping as a token of our appreciation for your patience. We assure you that we are taking the necessary steps to prevent such delays in the future.\n\nThank you for your understanding and continued trust in our products. We look forward to serving you better in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Your Company]  \n[Contact Information]",
